<h1> Estimate Macros </h1>

<p> Send us an image and/or a description of a meal and we'll ask AI to estimate how many calories and macronutrients it contains: </p>

<form action="/macro_results" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
  <div>
    <label for="image">Image </label>
    <input name="image_param" id="image" type="file" accept="image/*">
  </div>

  <div>
    <label for="words">Description </label>
    <textarea name="description_param" id="words"></textarea>
  </div>

  <button type="submit"> Estimate! </button>

</form>
